'''Helmholtz flow''' is a term used in [[fluid mechanics]] for flow with free [[Streamlines, streaklines, and pathlines|streamline]]s or [[vortex sheet]]s. <ref>[http://www.answers.com/topic/helmholtz-flow#ixzz21iyGxblc McGraw-Hill Dictionary of Scientific and Technical Terms] </ref>
