| caption                   = Sarfatti in November 2007
| birth_date                = {{Birth date and age|1939|9|14|mf=y}}<ref name=Schwartz5>Stephen Schwartz, [http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/SUNDAY-INTERVIEW-The-Universe-As-Seen-From-3774064.php "The Universe, As Seen From North Beach"], ''San Francisco Chronicle'', August 17, 1997, p.&nbsp;5.</ref> 
| birth_place               = [[Brooklyn, New York]]
